Description:
When you enter the building, a gentle receptionist flanked by a couple of guards informs you that this is a no-violence area. Everybody is welcome at Lady Zhi’s hot springs, where problems stay outside. You can enjoy the full hot springs experience for just 400g, as long as you don’t cause any trouble.

In this area, you find people from all walks of life: pirates, COT officers, natives, and free merchants.

It is a good place to rest, do some business, or listen to interesting stories.
DescriptionAction: Would you like to enjoy the services of the hot springs?
